                "content": "Susan is a branch manager at a bank. She decides to help her friend, Tom, who is having trouble opening an account in the UK. Tom is trying to bring funds in which he says are derived from his business ventures abroad. Susan gives Tom a personal reference and persuades an employee at her bank to waive the usually lengthy application process. As a result, Susan:",
