                "content": "<P>Susan's behaviour in this matter is highly inappropriate and the two offences of failing to make a report and assisting an offender may apply.</P><P><BR>She cannot be accused of tipping off as a report has not been made and the potential subject of the report has not been tipped off. Also, she cannot be charged with interfering with an investigation as an investigation is not currently in progress.</P>",
