                "content": "Hamid is an account manager. He recently discovered that a customer was buying and liquidating an unusual amount of investments and reported his suspicions to his firm's MLRO. The MLRO&#8217;s investigation showed that the transactions were perfectly legitimate. As a result, Hamid:",
